<p class="ayah 6-33" id="33" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَعْلَمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We know</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَيَحْزُنُكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">grieves you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَقُولُونَ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they say.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِنَّهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And indeed, they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُكَذِّبُونَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">deny you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَـٰكِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the wrongdoers -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِـَٔـايَـٰتِ ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Verses of Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span