 second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سُلَّمًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a ladder</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">into</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَآءِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the sky</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَتَأْتِيَهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so that you bring to them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِـَٔـايَةٍ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a Sign.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَآءَ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah (had) willed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَجَمَعَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">surely He (would) have gathered them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْهُدَىٰ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the guidance.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So (do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَكُونَنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><