ss="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُنَزِّلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">send down</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَايَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a Sign,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَـٰكِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَكْثَرَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">most of them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْلَمُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">know.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>37<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 6-38" id="38" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[of]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دَآبَّةٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">any animal</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَرْضِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the earth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">طَـٰٓئِرٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a bird</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَطِيرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(that) flies</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِجَنَاحَيْهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with its wings -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُمَمٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) communities</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْثَالُكُم‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">like you.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مّ