<p class="ayah 6-61" id="61" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقَاهِرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the Subjugator</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَوْقَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">over</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِبَادِهِۦ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">His slaves,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيُرْسِلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and He sends</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">over you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَفَظَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">guardians</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَتَّىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">until</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">comes</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَحَدَكُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) anyone of you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَوْتُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the death</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first