<p class="ayah 6-62" id="62" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رُدُّوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they are returned</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَوْلَـٰهُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their Protector -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحَقِّ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] True,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Unquestionably,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for Him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحُكْمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the judgment?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَسْرَعُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) swiftest</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحَـٰسِبِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(in taking) account.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class