anText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُبْسَلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is given up to destruction</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَفْسُۢ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a soul</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَسَبَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it (has) earned,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَيْسَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) for it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن دُونِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">besides</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلِىٌّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">any protector</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَفِيعٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">any intercessor.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَعْدِلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it offers ransom -</span></span>