<p class="ayah 6-71" id="71" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَدْعُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Shall we call</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن دُونِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">besides</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَنفَعُنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">benefits us</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَضُرُّنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">harms us,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَنُرَدُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and we turn back</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَعْقَابِنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">our heels</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَعْدَ</span>