class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱئْتِنَا‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Come to us.``</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُدَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Guidance</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْهُدَىٰ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the Guidance,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأُمِرْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and we have been commanded</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِنُسْلِمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that we submit</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِرَبِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to (the) Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعَـٰلَمِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the worlds</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>71<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 6-72" id="72" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَقِيمُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">establish</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّلَوٲةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the prayer</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱتَّقُوهُ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and fear Him.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the One</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَيْهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to Him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُحْشَرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you will be gathered.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>72<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
