<p class="ayah 6-74" id="74" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">۞ وَإِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">said</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِبْرَٲهِيمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Ibrahim</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِأَبِيهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to his father</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَازَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Aazar,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَتَتَّخِذُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Do you take</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَصْنَامًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">idols</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَالِهَةً‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(as) gods?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنِّىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, I</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَرَٮٰكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[I] see you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَوْمَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and your people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" d