<p class="ayah 6-75" id="75" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And thus</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نُرِىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We show(ed)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِبْرَٲهِيمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Ibrahim</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَلَكُوتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the kingdom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَرْضِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the earth,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلِيَكُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so that he would be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">among</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُوقِنِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the ones who are certain.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>75<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 6-76" id="76" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">covered</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">over him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّيْلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the night,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَءَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he saw</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَوْكَبًا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a star.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَـٰذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`This</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّى‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) my Lord.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَمَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَفَلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it set,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he said</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَآ أُحِبُّ</s