<p class="ayah 6-77" id="77" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">When</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَءَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he saw</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقَمَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the moon</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَازِغًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">rising</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَـٰذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`This</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّى‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) my Lord.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَمَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَفَلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it set</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَئِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`If</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(does) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَهْدِنِى</span><span class=