<p class="ayah 6-101" id="101" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَدِيعُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Originator</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَرْضِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the earth.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَّىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">How</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَكُونُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">can be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for Him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَدٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a son</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">while not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَكُن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(there) is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for Him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صَـٰحِبَةٌ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a companion,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَخَلَقَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and He created</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top firs