<p class="ayah 6-102" id="102" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَٲلِكُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">That</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبُّكُمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your Lord,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(there is) no</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَـٰهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">god</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُوَ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Him,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَـٰلِقُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Creator</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) every</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَىْءٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">thing,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱعْبُدُوهُ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so worship Him.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَ