<p class="ayah 6-108" id="108" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And (do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَسُبُّواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">insult</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those whom</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَدْعُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they invoke</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن دُونِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">other than</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَيَسُبُّواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">lest they insult</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَدْوَۢا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(in) enmity</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِغَيْرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">without</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِلْمٍ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">knowledge.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Thus</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top firs