cWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they were</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِيُؤْمِنُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">unless</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[that]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah wills.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَـٰكِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">But</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَكْثَرَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">most of them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَجْهَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) ignorant.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>111<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 6-112" id="112" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And thus</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَعَلْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We made</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِكُلِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for every</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَبِىٍّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Prophet</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَدُوًّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">an enemy -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَيَـٰطِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">devils</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْإِنسِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(from) the mankind</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْجِنِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the jinn,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُوحِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">inspiring</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَعْضُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">some of them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَعْضٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">others</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first r