<p class="ayah 6-126" id="126" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهَـٰذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And this</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صِرَٲطُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is the) way</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) your Lord -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُسْتَقِيمًا‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">straight.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Certainly</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَصَّلْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We have detailed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَيَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Verses</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِقَوْمٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for a people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَذَّكَّرُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">who take heed.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>126<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
