<p class="ayah 6-128" id="128" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And (the) Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَحْشُرُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He will gather them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَمِيعًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">all,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰمَعْشَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(and will say), `O assembly</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْجِنِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) [the] jinn!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Certainly,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱسْتَكْثَرْتُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you have (misled) many</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْإِنسِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the mankind.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَالَ أَوْلِيَآؤُهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And will say their friends</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">among</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْإِنسِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the men,</spa