<p class="ayah 6-129" id="129" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And thus</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نُوَلِّى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We make friends,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَعْضَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">some (of)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the wrongdoers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَعْضَۢا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) others</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they used to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَكْسِبُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">earn.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>129<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
