<p class="ayah 6-148" id="148" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَيَقُولُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Will say</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَشْرَكُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">associate partners (with Allah),</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`If</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَآءَ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah had willed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَشْرَكْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">we (would) have associated partners (with Allah)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَابَآؤُنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">our forefathers</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَرَّمْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">we (would) have forbidden</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[of]</span></sp