<p class="ayah 6-149" id="149" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلِلَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`With Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحُجَّةُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the argument -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْبَـٰلِغَةُ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the conclusive.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And if</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He (had) willed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهَدَٮٰكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">surely He (would) have guided you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَجْمَعِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">all.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>149<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
