<p class="ayah 6-151" id="151" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">۞ قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَعَالَوْاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Come,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَتْلُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">I will recite</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَرَّمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">has prohibited</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبُّكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْكُمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">That (do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُشْرِكُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">associate</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with Him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَيْــًٔا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">anything,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَبِٱلْوَٲلِدَيْنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and with the parents</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranT