what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ظَهَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) apparent</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَطَنَ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) concealed.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And (do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَقْتُلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">kill</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّفْسَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the soul</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّتِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">which</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَرَّمَ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah has forbidden</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْحَقِّ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by (legal) right.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَٲلِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">That</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَص