<p class="ayah 6-159" id="159" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَرَّقُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">divide</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دِينَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their religion</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَكَانُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and become</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شِيَعًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">sects,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّسْتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you are not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى شَىْءٍ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in anything.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّمَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Only</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْرُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their affair</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) with</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top fir