<p class="ayah 6-160" id="160" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">came</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْحَسَنَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with a good deed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then for him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَشْرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) ten (times)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْثَالِهَا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the like of it.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">came</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلسَّيِّئَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with an evil deed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُجْزَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he will be recompensed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span clas