<p class="ayah 6-161" id="161" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّنِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Indeed (as for) me,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هَدَٮٰنِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">has guided me</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبِّىٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">my Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صِرَٲطٍ مُّسْتَقِيمٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a straight path -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دِينًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a religion</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قِيَمًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">right,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّلَّةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">religion</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِبْرَٲهِيمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Ibrahim -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَنِيفًا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a true monotheist.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar